    org.tedros.api.presenter.behaviour.ITBehavior<M,​TDynaPresenter<M>>
    public class TMasterCrudViewBehavior<M extends TEntityModelView<E>,​E extends org.tedros.server.entity.ITEntity>
extends TDynaViewCrudBaseBehavior<M,​E>
    The behavior of the master detail view. This behavior can be applied on master entities with detail entities. A ListView with pagination is created to list the database result. It can be set using the TListViewPresenter annotation on the TEntityModelView. For entity processing, use TEjbService or TEntityProcess on TEntityModelView.
    Author:
    Davis Gordon
